HEADWORD: Doted
<hw>Dot"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Stupid;
foolish.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Senseless speech and <qex>doted</qex> ignorance.</q>
